GeoIP2-City-Test.mmdb is a synthetic test fixture from the MaxMind/MaxMind-DB
project (https://github.com/maxmind/MaxMind-DB/tree/main/test-data), included
here only to let the docker-compose dev environment exercise PowerDNS Lua
record geo functions (continent/country/region) locally.

It is NOT a real GeoIP database and must NOT be used in production.

